Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.92,0:00:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.37,0:00:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是個高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倖被歹徒灌下毒藥而變小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.34,0:00:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過雖然變小了 頭腦還是一樣的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個不摺不扣的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是發生在深夜的百貨公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打烊之後沒有人在樓層裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.18,0:00:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使夜是多麽的黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百貨公司挾持事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.10,0:01:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.82,0:01:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.78,0:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧 假面超人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.38,0:02:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把假面超人送嚮地獄去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.08,0:02:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的和平就由我"假面超人"來維護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.77,0:02:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把壞人一網打盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.10,0:02:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面回旋踢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.79,0:02:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回旋踢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.00,0:02:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽已經是高中生的我非得看這個不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你不喜歡假面超人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.09,0:02:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡了 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油…假面超人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.11,0:02:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.99,0:02:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝各位來賓 今天特地光臨本公司 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.54,0:02:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你們再次的光臨本公司 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.01,0:02:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.39,0:03:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人…正義的假面超人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.28,0:03:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人的簽名不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.31,0:03:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你弄丟了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.61,0:03:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想當一輩子的寶物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.95,0:03:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓我想想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.63,0:03:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得 跟假面超人照相的時候明明還在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.04,0:03:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 照片借我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.84,0:03:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那個時候元太確實是說他肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.71,0:03:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那個時候跑去買熱狗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.89,0:03:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放在那個攤位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.14,0:03:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去拿回來 你們去不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.93,0:03:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是百貨公司都快打烊了 今天就算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢夥真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.32,0:03:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正跟你沒有關係 我自己去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸給他們了 誰叫我沒事喜歡推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.73,0:04:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位快一點 還剩十分鍾保全係統就要開始啓動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.77,0:04:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 保全係統開始啓動的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說那個出入口也將會關閉的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要十分鍾我就可以拿到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見…辛苦你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.78,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.98,0:04:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.47,0:04:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.69,0:04:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我的寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多虧了柯南的名推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.17,0:04:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏…小事一樁而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快了 保全係統就快啓動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在該怎麽辦琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.99,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在就到店裏的警衛室去告訴他們實情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定會讓我們出去的 放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.76,0:05:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 警衛室是在地下二樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面超人! 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶石的專櫃是在六樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.17,0:05:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七樓的特別賣場裏面有古董品(翻譯錯請查實)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.38,0:05:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是電梯裏面的那個姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到天後之前 我們就慢慢地搜刮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強…強盜集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.99,0:05:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現的話就蹧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺掉的 快點逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.27,0:05:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那個電梯姐姐怎麽辦琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.97,0:05:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先不要讓他們發現我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 再去通知警察 知道了嗎琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.10,0:06:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 怎麽沒有發信的聲音琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話線被剪斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是 全部都被剪斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的電話應該可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 打不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.76,0:06:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店裏面職員專用的電話也已經被保全係統控制住了  
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 不會有人來救我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再被殺掉之前 還好我吃了很多的鳗魚便當了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.40,0:06:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就想要放棄 未免太早了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.42,0:06:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 快發現我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.60,0:06:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.31,0:06:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.31,0:06:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.45,0:06:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不能這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子會被強盜集團發現的 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 根本打不破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.89,0:07:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方的玻璃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.47,0:07:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用特別厚的玻璃做成的 打不破的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.28,0:07:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 切掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.77,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警衛室 七樓傳來的是什麽奇怪的聲音琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.02,0:07:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用七樓的防盜攝影機檢查看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.44,0:07:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是已經跟你說過 這樣是不行的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹧糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麽奇怪的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說沒有異常琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 剛剛明明聽到那邊有聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.96,0:08:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點 快把寶石拿起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.15,0:08:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了慎重起見 過去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.71,0:08:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 出口到底在哪裏琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.25,0:08:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聲一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.76,0:08:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.52,0:08:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.95,0:08:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.17,0:08:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我回來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我剛才跟園子聊天聊太久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去做飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉被看到了 全部都給我抓起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 大傢坐到上面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警衛室 聽到了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.74,0:09:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把燈打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麽 我聽不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.58,0:09:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鬼頭 這裏有小鬼頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼 我看你們跑到哪裏去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽回事琺 喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽回事 發生什麽事了琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在警衛室裏面的歹徒已經發現了我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.26,0:09:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他們爲了要抓住我們 把燈全部打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.73,0:09:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 我們趕快離開這裏吧! 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.54,0:09:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.90,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.39,0:10:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南他人呢 他怎麽到現在還沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.39,0:10:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麽知道會發生那種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.77,0:10:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的正是時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 出來 大傢都出來 快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.63,0:10:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點點我們就會全被關在電梯裏頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.96,0:10:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我們安全離開這裏以後再嚮我道謝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南今天應該是去百貨公司了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.26,0:10:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該是跟那些小傢夥一塊兒去看玩偶秀了吧 不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 現在天都已經黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話去百貨公司問問看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.96,0:11:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管那個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.10,0:11:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的晚餐做好了沒有 你想要餓死我是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 這裏是丸丹百貨公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.72,0:11:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的營業已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.99,0:11:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 總而言之 我們一定要離那些傢夥遠一點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.70,0:11:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.93,0:11:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天跟平常一樣上午十點開始營業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是已經說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了 趕快去煮我的飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這次又是要打到哪兒去琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 對不起 我是毛利蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.98,0:11:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那聲音是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是元太他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 你就躲在這個地方不要出來  知不知道 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.83,0:12:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他兩個人在什麽地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 我還不想死 救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.71,0:12:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是警察 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢百貨公司已經被我們包圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.71,0:12:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經逃不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的把武器丟掉 放開小孩子 聽到沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊…快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鬼 只有一群小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.08,0:12:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 那些臭小鬼竟然用模特兒來騙我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 請問是吉田公館嗎琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是江戶川柯南的傢人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 步美她也還沒有回傢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.36,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說 剛才光彥的傢人也有打電話過來問了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 到底發生什麽事情了琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 元太 難道你想被歹徒給抓走嗎琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麽了嗎 柯南琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了拿什麽東西了 是不是琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.86,0:13:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是…不是這樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的腦海裏好像被什麽東西卡住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.70,0:13:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麽東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁架 是柯南 他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下這個原因了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.78,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.48,0:14:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的孩子傢裏面有沒有接到付贖金的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜 他們應該是在某個地方逗留了一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.26,0:14:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定馬上就會回來的 別緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.10,0:14:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 現在可以去煮飯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你不要太過份了 好不好 去煮飯給我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 請問是搜查一課嗎 目暮警官他在不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很意外的 進行的很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.06,0:14:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候 你真傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.68,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在沒有辦法因爲我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.80,0:15:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思這麽晚了真是非常的抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.68,0:15:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.13,0:15:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.27,0:15:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還不能說孩子們被卷入了什麽事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 到現在都還沒有回傢的確是蠻奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們果然是出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之在轄區內我會做好安排的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 馬上就會找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常的謝謝您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了 我另外還有要事正在處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.36,0:15:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就先告辭了 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽一來應該做的也做完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下的就等候報告而已了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.89,0:15:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去吃飯吧 吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.82,0:15:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情我以前就很想做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.34,0:15:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我們得救之後一定會付錢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我們真的可以得救嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.95,0:16:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽連元太都哭喪著臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.18,0:16:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都已經吃飽了 大傢打起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.90,0:16:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先把那些傢夥全打敗再從這裏出去 一定可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我們少年偵探團的名義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.76,0:16:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.68,0:16:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的名義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開會能開到這種時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.68,0:16:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定是相當重要的事件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前爲止 柯南他們還行蹤不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就不重要了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都是柯南這小傢夥害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.69,0:16:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我連飯都吃不到了 真是要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強盜集團趁百貨公司打烊之後潛入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.26,0:16:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將寶石還有電器制品等等搜刮一空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.73,0:16:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官所說的要事該不會就是指這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.08,0:17:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百貨公司 難道是琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.45,0:17:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來 小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始還擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次看你們躲哪兒去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.04,0:17:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.71,0:17:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最不擅長喝酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.45,0:17:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.01,0:17:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.76,0:18:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍無可忍了 不能讓你們活下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對動物最沒有辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.00,0:18:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.51,0:18:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.03,0:18:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.17,0:18:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰 在那裏的人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 電梯裏面的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友 你怎麽會在這裏琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之待在這裏是很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有很多壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.68,0:19:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 跟姐姐一起逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不需要再假裝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部知道了電梯裏的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 應該說是強盜集團的第五位成員小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.24,0:19:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 能讓電梯移動的人就是第五個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.72,0:19:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她正等著我們全部到齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而留在警衛室的人們當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我們有幾個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就只有你而已了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.82,0:19:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你就以電梯小姐的身份混進了這傢百貨公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時進行偵探還有引導地工作 對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你到底是什麽人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是江戶川柯南 是一個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的推理果然高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.01,0:20:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.17,0:20:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用那種武器太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 把她引誘到屋頂上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用的 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.86,0:20:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有籃球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.60,0:20:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做無謂的掙紮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.67,0:20:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.37,0:21:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.16,0:21:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢夥就是強盜集團的份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.68,0:21:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們全帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們全部睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.39,0:21:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是輸給他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.74,0:23:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天 我們因爲逮捕了強盜集團而受到表揚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.42,0:23:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在食品賣場中吃的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.38,0:23:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有在賣場所破壞的商品沒有被追究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.63,0:23:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.09,0:23:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.34,0:23:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是少年偵探團的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.47,0:23:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.70,0:24:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麽了事琺剛才的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.12,0:24:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老師的房間裏發出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.03,0:24:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.50,0:24:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來，我們拍了錄像帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.86,0:24:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽琺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.94,0:24:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說..說不定這個拍下了犯人犯罪的經過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.13,0:24:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓老師的禮服染上鮮血的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.35,0:24:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.95,0:24:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.08,0:24:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六月新娘殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.91,0:24:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.81,0:24:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠囊藥丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.96,0:24:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集也是相當的難解呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.76,0:00:21.19,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔百年的世紀末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.85,0:00:27.40,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在應該流淚的時候我卻笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.51,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔太久太久的世紀末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.62,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我飛奔嚮廣闊無邊的新世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.13,0:00:52.15,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些在我孩童時代還一知半解的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.30,0:00:58.59,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在長大以後還是這樣不太明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.89,0:01:01.59,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麽了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.85,0:01:04.60,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更算不上是出色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.85,0:01:11.02,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所知道的只有 心裏忐忑不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.15,0:01:16.90,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是答案 也並非是真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.95,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所相信的是 只有心的悸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.21,0:01:28.45,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裏的忐忑和不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.20,0:22:16.55,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我的想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.75,0:22:21.17,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝著涼了一半的紅茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.44,0:22:26.31,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄著纏繞在手指上的細繩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.09,0:22:35.31,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴著BOSSA NOVO的節奏腳歩變得輕快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.51,0:22:40.32,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎底就在我手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.61,0:22:46.62,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 Ah- Ah- Ah-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.80,0:22:56.46,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的裝束 相同的地點 下週我也會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.85,0:22:58.97,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步接一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.15,0:23:03.89,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必對他心生厭倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.86,0:23:06.01,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個案件接一個案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.22,0:23:10.31,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎爾是否笑話我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.76,0:23:15.40,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無盡的日子以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.58,0:23:20.02,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有他在等待著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.50,0:23:24.57,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走我自己的路
